pr_body:
Translate all occurrences of "instructions" with "Anleitung" instead of "Instruktionen" to sound less technical;
translate "account" with "Konto" consistently;
translate "login" was translated with "anmelden" or "Anmledung" consistently;
Connect "E-Mail-Adresse" with dashes.

@mk-fg -- I was designing a config system and came up with a design identical to yours. Found this repo when I was searching for AttrDict implementations for YAML.

If you don't mind, I'd like to help with the maintenance of this repository -- documentation, test cases, PEP8 fixes, etc to begin with. I'd rather work with your code than maintain a separate fork.

This is a pull request to make the code mostly PEP8 compliant (via `autopep8` and a few manual edits.) Will send some test cases and doc updates over the next few days.

FFD should ProcessRouteTLV when HandleChildIdResponse() and only FFD need to consider whether to BecomeRouter() or not;
REED should also ProcessRouteTLV when HandleAdvertisement() from neighbors.

@jwhui , would you please help to have a review?
